parameters: Ceres: Please let me through there~.

[Guard] No way. Absolutely not. It's the same no matter how many times
you come.
Ceres: Sir, I have some fine liquor here.
[Guard] Even if you bring a gift, it's no good.
Ceres: Geez, you're stubborn. A true mark of a fine guard.
Ceres: Yo! Future head of the guard squad!

[Guard] Beyond here are Lady Lucia and the Valentinas. I can't let a
filthy rat like you in. Scram. Shoo!

Ceres: If it isn't Luuna. The genius sorceress of the imperial capital
Jupiterino.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lord Ceres! I'm being pursued! This way!
